    "scopeAndContentNote": "This film contains aerial coverage of a flight of Atlas F (Test 103) at the Atlantic Missile Range. It shows the missile in flight, then breaking up, with the camera holding on the nose cone, with a smaller object in flight above and behind the nose cone on a parallel path. (Note: one experiment aboard Test 103 was decoy nose cone.)",
